{"tid":1584791,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Blockchain 公投系統有冇得諗","createTime":"2019-09-21T10:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T22:14:45.000Z","uid":149978,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"504725722b9860a3294f59d6a74aa4e07809f1a7","tid":1584791,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:05:39.000Z","msg":"前言：目前政府冇公投，但有很多具爭議性的議題<br />\n例如：逃犯修例修訂、一地兩檢等<br />\n<br />\n民間有很多網站搞投票，可惜公信力成疑問<br />\n<br />\n目前電腦界開始冒起左 Blockchain<br />\nBlockchain 並非Bitcoin, 但Bitcoin 探用了Blockchain 並使它流行<br />\nBlockchain係一個去中央化的記帳系統<br />\n記帳系統內容可完全公開<br />\n且帳目靠去<strong>程式碼公開、去中心化、加密技術</strong>，達至<strong>無法刪改</strong>，<strong>可全民監控</strong>的資料庫。<br />\n<br />\n目前有個咁的Technical idea<br />\n<br />\n驗證：用 Mobile + SMS 或用 IP , Hash後對VerifiedHashKey <br />\n<br />\n投票網：網頁碼程式上 Github<br />\n<br />\nBlockchain Database: (以下假設用 MOBILE NO)<br />\nTable: RegisteredUser<br />\nUserID<br />\nVerifiedHashKey = SHA512(MobileNo + Salt), <br />\nSalt = 512-bit Salt Random Generated by System<br />\n<br />\nTable: VoteTopic<br />\nVoteID<br />\nVoteTopic<br />\nVoteDescription<br />\n<br />\nTable: VoteResult<br />\nUserID<br />\nVoteID<br />\nVoteResult"},{"pid":"0ddceb0852f2420a3d1425ecba94409615b694b6","tid":1584791,"uid":293619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"504725722b9860a3294f59d6a74aa4e07809f1a7","tid":1584791,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:05:39.000Z","msg":"前言：目前政府冇公投，但有很多具爭議性的議題<br />\n例如：逃犯修例修訂、一地兩檢等<br />\n<br />\n民間有很多網站搞投票，可惜公信力成疑問<br />\n<br />\n目前電腦界開始冒起左 Blockchain<br />\nBlockchain 並非Bitcoin, 但Bitcoin 探用了Blockchain 並使它流行<br />\nBlockchain係一個去中央化的記帳系統<br />\n記帳系統內容可完全公開<br />\n且帳目靠去<strong>程式碼公開、去中心化、加密技術</strong>，達至<strong>無法刪改</strong>，<strong>可全民監控</strong>的資料庫。<br />\n<br />\n目前有個咁的Technical idea<br />\n<br />\n驗證：用 Mobile + SMS 或用 IP , Hash後對VerifiedHashKey <br />\n<br />\n投票網：網頁碼程式上 Github<br />\n<br />\nBlockchain Database: (以下假設用 MOBILE NO)<br />\nTable: RegisteredUser<br />\nUserID<br />\nVerifiedHashKey = SHA512(MobileNo + Salt), <br />\nSalt = 512-bit Salt Random Generated by System<br />\n<br />\nTable: VoteTopic<br />\nVoteID<br />\nVoteTopic<br />\nVoteDescription<br />\n<br />\nTable: VoteResult<br />\nUserID<br />\nVoteID<br />\nVoteResult"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:09:10.000Z","msg":"唔識 program<br />\n但好似好勁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564d2ff43de14026c138df6ee3a20079dc8087e8","tid":1584791,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:11:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"57be203fb97c839955ce1a6e8b577af04c79be9d","tid":1584791,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:13:53.000Z","msg":"好似要咁好些<br />\n<strong>Public Program</strong><br />\nAll code except salt.key , other password and config<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Private Program</strong><br />\nFile salt.key <br />\nSalt = 512-bit Salt (keep by webadmin)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Blockchain Database</strong><br />\nTable: <ins>RegisteredUser</ins><br />\nUserID,<br />\nVerifiedHashKey = SHA512(MobileNo + Salt)<br />\n<br />\nTable: <ins>VoteTopic</ins><br />\nVoteID,<br />\nVoteTopic,<br />\nVoteDescription<br />\n<br />\nTable: <ins>VoteResult</ins><br />\nUserID,<br />\nVoteID,<br />\nVoteResult"},{"pid":"f691773c3e526352f9c51bbc1800626a9ecd8993","tid":1584791,"uid":214672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:17:17.000Z","msg":"可以 用埋cryptocurrency 可以廢埋港紙"},{"pid":"ab5e6008d757faaf1b1e915d0b53576e86746a43","tid":1584791,"uid":170252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc