出18年都無法有人成功可以破解到1個的SHA256/SHA512 HASH"},{"pid":"7b200afee8a37bb1967ec293e98fa58947c43f3c","tid":1584791,"uid":64963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:45:06.000Z","msg":"你點樣認證你個手機number 係真實"},{"pid":"8bb10c09867d8110c86d4c7d193e95b257f8dd25","tid":1584791,"uid":64963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b200afee8a37bb1967ec293e98fa58947c43f3c","tid":1584791,"uid":64963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:45:06.000Z","msg":"你點樣認證你個手機number 係真實"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:46:46.000Z","msg":"如果我求其用8個number 加salt 去申請 點證明我果8個number 係屬於我個手機號碼"},{"pid":"5e47b993ca7f031830049466e49407c70b0b8246","tid":1584791,"uid":170252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ae38ac3f6f65b803b38aa0425a97a8eeb8b7e3f","tid":1584791,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0363fd9267b3c34dcc6bcf991aa36fb176c460b","tid":1584791,"uid":170252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ef0a7ded1d4e3cbbc651d9eb158965bb92c16a5","tid":1584791,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:22:46.000Z","msg":"ISP email / University email 都OK<br />\n<br />\nCertificate 香港有幾多人有用 / 識用 ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:28:05.000Z","msg":"你睇連登幾多cd rom就知道有幾多人無isp /u email. 同埋，isp/u email每人可以有多過一個(利申我都有兩個)。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:31:53.000Z","msg":"投票一定要有id先確保難啲洗到票<br />\n一個唔該你收集到啲id去送中咁點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:46:53.000Z","msg":"所以就要用certificate, 相當於一個hash咗既id."},{"pid":"290a260ecc15a73d7bac39eb68fe746865015cd0","tid":1584791,"uid":170252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e47b993ca7f031830049466e49407c70b0b8246","tid":1584791,"uid":170252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ae38ac3f6f65b803b38aa0425a97a8eeb8b7e3f","tid":1584791,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0363fd9267b3c34dcc6bcf991aa36fb176c460b","tid":1584791,"uid":170252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score